dct_title_s: Γεογραφικος Χαρτης της  νεας Ελλάδος / σύνταχοεισ νπο Ρ. Κιπερτ και Ο. Μελχιγγ ; Εκδοτικος οικος “Ελευθοερουσακς ”. (Sheet 4)
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading and spot heights. Depths shown by isolines. Includes inset: [Cyprus]. Includes inset of Κύπρος [Cyprus] Prime meridian: Athens. Nomoi [prefectures] are listed and located. Map shows roads, railroads, sea routes, and lighthouses. Index map on verso. Companion volume call number location:  GA84 .K446 1921q. Stored in ReCap. Princeton copy is from the library of Alison Frantz, gift of John M. Camp II, *77.
